Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,STAND UP まだ僕を呼んでる声が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:03.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,「YES」だって「NO」だって 関係はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:08.33,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 穴だらけのゲームスコア
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:13.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE　自由を見たくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 閉ざされた夜に I'll be eaten away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,透明な武器を手に入れてる LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんの為に　何を守る　長い待ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:33.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぶち壞すこの彈丸で！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:38.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE モノクロな光のない世界でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE　心は染まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:49.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD　絕望に僅かな希望握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:58.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,震える指で狙い定めて 未來を探せ！
Comment: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:53.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————OPCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STAND UP 呼喚我的聲音未絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:03.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論答案是「YES」或「NO」 都沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:08.33,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 遊戲結果已滿是漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:13.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE 希冀能看到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 在這憋悶的夜晚 我終將被腐蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無形的武器已然到手 LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了什麼 要守護什麼 才經過漫長等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:33.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這顆子彈破壞一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:38.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE 即使在這僅剩黑白 暗無光輝的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE 心靈絕不沾染黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:49.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在絕望中握住僅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:58.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用顫抖的手指瞄準目標 去追尋未來！
Comment: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:25.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:35.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:40.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:46.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:50.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:56.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:23:01.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:11.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:11.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:35.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
Comment: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:25.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:35.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴隨著結尾即開始的詠嘆調
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:40.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高舉白旗的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:46.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃獄後的歡呼聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:50.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:56.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:23:01.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:11.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:11.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撥開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒绝喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:35.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都愛著绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會滿懷悲傷地離去
